  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>Shall I\n        at least ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>Cf. Isaiah 38.1: \"Thus saith the Lord, Set thine\n        house in order; for thou shalt die, and not live.\"\n        The inclusive \"I,\" who sits in the symbolic act\n        of fishing (seeking salvation, regeneration, eternity)\n        with the Waste Land behind him, wonders how far he can\n        order his affairs. </p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
